// TestCategoryC_CorruptionBeforeCommit verifies handling of corruption that
// occurs after data write but before commit record completion.
//
// VERIFICATION GOALS:
// - Uncommitted transaction detected as incomplete
// - Recovery replays incomplete transaction safely
