// - No orphaned extents left in pool
//
// FAILURE SCENARIOS:
// - WriteFile proceeds through DataWritten state
// - Corrupt extent data before commit record finalized
// - Kill process to simulate crash mid-commit
//
// EXPECTED OUTCOMES:
// - Recovery detects incomplete transaction
// - Replay either completes or rolls back cleanly
// - File is either fully written or not visible
