// - File remains readable after repair
//
// FAILURE SCENARIOS:
// - Write file successfully and close coordinator
// - Corrupt extent file on disk after commit
// - Reopen coordinator and run scrub
//
// EXPECTED OUTCOMES:
// - Scrub detects post-commit corruption
// - Repair transaction created (not replay)
